android.car

类 CarFeatures

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.car.CarFeatures

  • public final class CarFeatures
extends java.lang.Object
    This class declares all car features which does not have API as String.

    Note that all Car*Managers' feature string is their service name Car.*_SERVICE. For features with APIs, subfeature String will be also defined inside the API.

    To prevent potential conflict in feature / subfeature name, all feature name should use implementation package name space like com.android.car.user.FeatureA unless it is Car.*_SERVICE.

    To define a subfeature, main feature should be already declared and sub feature name should have the format of "main_feature/sub_feature_name". Note that feature name cannot use '/' and should use only alphabet, digit, '_', '-' and '.'.
